Introduction
============

A simple time keeping tool for the pomodro tequnique.

Requirements
------------
This is an application written for/with PyQt4. This has to be installed seperately and cannot be installed via pip or easy_install. 

Features
--------
- only starts one instance
- tbA

Usage
-----
Normal usage:
```
m4pomodoro 
```

The following is meant for usage from the i3blocks (i3wm statusbar).
```
m4pomodoro --action i3blocks 
```
